They are people too so you can just try to understand what they feel when you say some sad things and they will try to understand your feelings. how annoying is such a selfish influence on people like you.  You are just a lonely person who wanted to be like everyone else, but these freaks only think about themselves.  It is good that this situation did not continue.  I also have problems that constantly get into my head when I think about relationships with people, and it's just awful.  You are still very young and your problems will surely pass over time, so do not be upset, you still have a future. Maybe it wasn't helpful, but I still hope you'll listen to my words.  All the best to you, good luck, stay cool.
